author: chris-dollin
msg: Refactored some code so that there is less duplication between the
"normal" and "faster" GraphMem. The intention is to drive toward
reducing the difference as much as possible, so that there's less to
test (the "faster" code doesn't have all the tests it should at the
moment, so anything that can be shared with the "normal" code is good).
